<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AI Evolution Timeline | Portfolio</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #0b0f19;
            --card-bg: #1e293b;
            --accent-color: #38bdf8;
            --text-main: #f8fafc;
            --text-muted: #94a3b8;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-main);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        header h1 {
            color: var(--accent-color);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        header p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        /* Timeline Container */
        .timeline {
            position: relative;
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 100%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        /* Main Vertical Line */
        .timeline::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 4px;
            background-color: var(--card-bg);
            top: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 50%;
            margin-left: -2px;
        }

        /* Timeline Items */
        .container {
            padding: 10px 40px;
            position: relative;
            background-color: inherit;
            width: 50%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        /* Dots on the line */
        .container::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            right: -8px;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            border: 4px solid var(--accent-color);
            top: 25px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .left { left: 0; }
        .right { left: 50%; }

        .right::after { left: -8px; }

        /* Content Cards */
        .content {
            padding: 20px 30px;
            background-color: var(--card-bg);
            position: relative;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-color);
        }

        .right .content {
            border-left: none;
            border-right: 4px solid var(--accent-color);
        }

        .date {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--accent-color);
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .content h3 {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }

        .content p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin: 10px 0 0 0;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .timeline::after { left: 31px; }
            .container { width: 100%; padding-left: 70px; padding-right: 25px; }
            .container::after { left: 23px; }
            .left::after, .right::after { left: 23px; }
            .right { left: 0%; }
            .content { border-right: none !important; border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-color) !important; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>The Evolution of Artificial Intelligence</h1>
        <p>A curated professional timeline mapping key algorithmic milestones and paradigm shifts in machine learning.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="timeline">
        
        <!-- Milestone 1 -->
        <div class="container left">
            <div class="content">
                <div class="date">1950s - 1980s</div>
                <h3>Foundations & Symbolic AI</h3>
                <p>Early exploration focused on symbolic logic, rule-based expert systems, and the initial concepts of neural pathways.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Milestone 2 -->
        <div class="container right">
            <div class="content">
                <div class="date">2012</div>
                <h3>The Deep Learning Boom</h3>
                <p>AlexNet wins the ImageNet competition, proving the power of Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) scaled with GPUs.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Milestone 3 -->
        <div class="container left">
            <div class="content">
                <div class="date">2017</div>
                <h3>The Transformer Paradigm</h3>
                <p>Introduction of the "Attention Is All You Need" architecture, completely revolutionizing Natural Language Processing.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Milestone 4 -->
        <div class="container right">
            <div class="content">
                <div class="date">Present Day</div>
                <h3>Generative AI & Agents</h3>
                <p>The scaling of Foundational LLMs and multimodal systems transitioning into highly autonomous agentic workflows.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

</body>
</html>
